snippet.title: I Am Your Beast - 'TYRANTS BETTER RUN' TRAILER
snippet.description:
Hear "Tyrants Better Run" in the hot new indie FPS I Am Your Beast, coming to PC on August 15th and iOS on November 19th! From the developers of El Paso, Elsewhere and Clickolding.
